This paper discusses the development of in-database analytics, which is a topic related to database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses statistical data analysis and performance optimization, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses the integration of analytics techniques into RDBMS, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
